    • addDevelopmentCard

      public void addDevelopmentCard​(int pos, DevelopmentCard card) throws PositionInvalidException, IndexOutOfSlotDevelopmentCardsException
      This method adds a development card into an available slot, then check if is the seventh and in the end update the array of cards on top
      Parameters:
      pos - : column where the card is going to be added
      card - : card that is going to be added
      Throws:
      PositionInvalidException - propagates this exception, generated if the position requested is occupied or there are no card under with lower level in the same position
      IndexOutOfSlotDevelopmentCardsException - if you are out of bound of slots for development cards
